column16: Erick Aybar pops out to shortstop Yunel Escobar.
Alberto Callaspo reaches on fielding error by pitcher Scott Richmond.    Kendrys Morales to 3rd.    Howard Kendrick to 2nd.
Howard Kendrick singles on a ground ball to center fielder Colby Rasmus.    Kendrys Morales to 2nd.
Kendrys Morales grounds into a force out, first baseman Adam Lind to shortstop Yunel Escobar.    Albert Pujols scores.    Peter Bourjos out at 2nd.    Kendrys Morales to 1st.
Peter Bourjos singles on a ground ball to left fielder Edwin Encarnacion.    Mike Trout scores.    Albert Pujols to 2nd.
Torii Hunter singles on a ground ball to shortstop Yunel Escobar.
Mike Trout strikes out on foul tip.
John Hester homers (3) on a fly ball to left field.   Erick Aybar scores.
Erick Aybar singles on a line drive to center fielder Colby Rasmus.
Howard Kendrick flies out to right fielder Jose Bautista.
Alberto Callaspo grounds out, second baseman Kelly Johnson to first baseman Adam Lind.
Mark Trumbo grounds out, shortstop Yunel Escobar to first baseman Adam Lind.
Ryan Kalish flies out to center fielder Colby Rasmus.
Will Middlebrooks out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Jose Bautista.    Cody Ross scores.    Adrian Gonzalez to 3rd on the throw.
